headline: DGX Stock Gains Following the Launch of New AD-Detect Blood Test
summary: Quest Diagnostics introduces AD-Detect Abeta, a new laboratory blood test, to detect Alzheimer's disease without any PET imaging and cerebral spinal fluid testing.
